{"word":"Ἀγυιεύς","slug":"Ἀγυιεύς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Ἀγυιεύς</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀγυιά'><el>ἀγυιά</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>name of Apollo, <i>guardian of the streets</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a pillar set up at</i> the street door, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}